Dana Hill https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dana_Hill 0 Dana Hill (born Dana Lynne Goetz; May 6, 1964 – July 15, 1996) was an American actress. Hill is best known for having played Audrey Griswold in National Lampoon’s European Vacation, and also known for her roles in Shoot the Moon and Cross Creek.
